Introduction

She’Z (Korean: 쉬즈) was a four-member girl group formed by Line Entertainment. They made their official debut on May 17, 2012, with the digital single “She’z Holic”. Before this, they contributed to the soundtrack of the drama Scent of a Woman OST.
